{"tid":1135111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"博出位？外籍男硬開車門　拍片女友讚：變形俠醫","createTime":"2019-05-02T06:05:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T01:39:03.000Z","uid":225464,"like":9,"dislike":509,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"128ae1754fe29d572dafe07b8ba013901d704123","tid":1135111,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:05:01.000Z","msg":"博出位？外籍男硬開車門 拍片女友讚：變形俠醫<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2DKnG68\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2DKnG68&d=5W7Dp6DGRi9eT2AMHrnJu0PYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=260433fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2DKnG68</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190502/photo/bkn-20190502133120906-0502_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190502140134\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190502%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190502133120906-0502_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190502140134&h=307d1ed9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真係以為咁做好型？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n片段星期三（1日）於網上瘋傳，只見當時有港鐵列車正在關門，有外籍男子突然急奔至車門前，先用力拉開月台幕門，再將已緊閉的列車車門強行扯開，與拍攝的同行友人一起步入車廂。車廂內的乘客均睇到目瞪口呆。片主在貼文中用英文大讚︰「發現變形俠醫！這是我的男朋友」。"},{"pid":"17b5fa28f0725438eee1d84418f2b6444befe0b9","tid":1135111,"uid":16676,"like":134,"dislike":3,"score":131,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:07:08.000Z","msg":"刀片<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dc9c0d46351dd77f467bb1ff9df4983768922d3","tid":1135111,"uid":50502,"like":16,"dislike":107,"score":-91,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:08:42.000Z","msg":"中國人特別戇鳩"},{"pid":"dccbbc50fafb8a4b9a4c47f4d664841b308b5221","tid":1135111,"uid":35699,"like":107,"dislike":1,"score":106,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:08:51.000Z","msg":"下次去觀塘線開啲大陸車嘛"},{"pid":"fc90070e94d84fd771c86ad7933721171e38e08a","tid":1135111,"uid":1637,"like":11,"dislike":5,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:26:05.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"5f40b1228f180d4fa0ba0dac40108c08f5501f3a","tid":1135111,"uid":18249